<h3><a id="10" name="10" pa-marked="1"></a>10.&nbsp;Can Children Use Our Services?</h3> <p>The Sites and Services are not directed to children under the age of 13. &nbsp;We do not knowingly collect information, including Personal Data, from children or other individuals who are not legally able to use our Sites and Services. If we obtain actual knowledge that we have collected Personal Data from a child under the age of 13, we will promptly delete it, unless we are legally obligated to retain such data. <a href="https://www.paypal.com/webapps/mpp/ua/privacy-full#12" pa-marked="1">Contact us</a> if you believe that we have mistakenly or unintentionally collected information from a child under the age of 13.</p> 

